            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Settings now load correctly — tolerant decoder handles missing/unknown JSON keys</li>
                    <li>Hooks display properly — fixed decoder for string matchers, timeout, new hook types</li>
                    <li>Redesigned hooks UI — collapsed empty sections, sheet editor with clear labels</li>
                    <li>Accurate storage stats — total includes all of ~/.claude/, message counts exclude events</li>
                    <li>No more defaults flash on navigation</li>
