        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.7</title>
            <sparkle:version>13</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>13 CLAUDE.md templates organized by category (iOS, Android, Next.js, Python, Go, Rust, Monorepo, etc.)</li>
                    <li>Auto-backup before applying a template — restore from backup button in toolbar</li>
                    <li>Search now shows sub-sections and scrolls directly to the matched setting</li>
                    <li>Expanded search keywords — Fast Mode, shell, memory, voice, and many more now findable</li>
                    <li>Fixed settings reset on new install (guarded all onChange handlers)</li>
                    <li>Fixed sidebar ghost items and section headers during search</li>
                    <li>Fixed search crash when clearing text</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2026 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
